<h5>If I&rsquo;m a Consumer and I'm ordering from outside Australia &ndash; What do I do?</h5>
<p>Cengage Learning Australia has the distribution rights for the following countries: Australia, Papua New Guinea (PNG), Fiji and NZ.<br />
<br />
At the moment our website can only service our Australian and NZ customers, but as part of the future development of this website our customers from PNG and FIJI will be able to order online.<br />
<br />
If you are from PNG or FIJI and wish to place an order please contact <a href="/contact-us">Customer Service</a><br />
<br />
For customers ordering from other countries click<a href="/about-us"> About Us</a> for information on other Cengage companies.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
</p>
<h5>Why don&rsquo;t you deliver to PO boxes?</h5>
<p>To ensure that your order is received and delivered in full it is essential that we provide our nominated transport company with a street address.<br />
<br />
If you are from a remote area or cannot provide a street address please contact<a href="/contact-us"> Customer Service</a> for assistance with your order.<br />
<br />
</p>
<h5>Do you supply large format text or audio for people who are Visually Impaired?&nbsp;</h5>
<p>Yes we do! Please visit our Accessibility Requests page.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
Are my credit card details private and secure?<br />
This website has been constructed in accordance with the new provisions of the Privacy Amendment (Private Sector) Act 2000.<br />
Read our Privacy policy for more details.<br />
<br />
</p>
<h5>What are the terms and conditions of sale?</h5>
<p>Our Terms and Conditions of Sale must be read and accepted by all Consumer and Business customers who purchase any of our Cengage Learning Australia website products. Click <a href="/corporate-home/help/terms-and-conditions">Terms and Conditions</a> for more details.<br />
<br />
</p>
