</p>
<h5>What is a promotional code?</h5>
<p>This code is located on all of our Cengage Learning Australia promotion material. A promotional code ensures that any special price or discount that may be offered on a promotion will be populated to your order. Please be aware, promotional offers may have expiry dates.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
</p>
<h5>Where do I find the promotional code?</h5>
<p>On the online order form located under the email address on the first page.<br />
<br />
</p>
